com.novell.ldapchai
Interface ChaiConstant

public interface ChaiConstant

Constants used by the Chai API. In general, it is encouraged to use the constants defined here for attribute names instead of arbitrary strings. For example:

Discouraged

    chaiUser.readStringAttribute("givenName");

Recommended

    chaiUser.readStringAttribute(ChaiConstant.ATTR_LDAP_GIVEN_NAME);

See the Constant Field Definitions for a list of actual values.

Author:
Jason D. Rivard
